            <p>The two nouns in the problem description above, <term>Student</term> and <term>Course</term> would make good class names! Then, you can think about what data you need to keep track of for students and courses and what methods you need. For example, for the Student class, you might need to keep track of the student’s name and grade level. For the Course class, you might need to keep track of the course name and the teacher’s name. What other attributes did you and your classmates come up with?</p>
